Standards-Version: 3.6.2.0
Build-Depends-Indep: cdbs (>= 0.4.34), debhelper (>= 5.0.7), python-dev (>= 2.4)

Package: hwtest
Architecture: all
Depends: python (>= 2.4), hwtest-lib
Description: Hardware test
 This project provides an interface for gathering hardware details
 and prompting the user for questions. This information can then be
 sent to Launchpad.

Package: hwtest-lib
Section: python
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, python-dbus | python2.4-dbus, python-apt | python2.4-apt, hal, fping, xbase-clients, libxrandr2
Description: Hardware test library
 This python package provides high-level functions for managing
 hwtest questions

