Architecture: all
Depends: python (>= 2.4), hwtest-lib, python-gtk2, python-glade2, hwtest
Description: GTK frontend for the hwtest program
 This project provides an interface for gathering hardware details
 and prompting the user for questions. This information can then be
 sent to Launchpad.
 .
 This package provides a GTK frontend for answering questions.
